          "name": "What Are Diamonds?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Are Diamonds?</h2><p>Diamonds are naturally formed carbon crystals produced under intense heat and pressure deep within the earth. They are prized for their brilliance, hardness, and symbolic meaning. Diamonds also come in various forms from classic engagement stones to designs like cocktail rings diamond, where size and boldness add to the final cost.</p>",
